          "subtitle": "Core lessons to carry forward",
          "slidecontent": "• AI confidence scores can mislead\n• High probability does not mean certain\n• Always verify before acting\n• Context shapes prediction accuracy\n• Question outputs, not just results\n• Seek human oversight always"
